Product: Xiaomi Redmi Note 9 Pro 64GB / 6GB RAM 6.53" LTE GSM 64MP Factory Unlocked Smartphone - Global Model - Interstellar Grey
Name: John
Comment: This is a great phone for the price. Nice big screen, great camera, charges very fast, easy to transfer apps from old phone, and good sound. The only drawback was finding a carrier. After a lot of research and head banging I called support and they recommended T-Mobile. Got T-Mobile and it gets 4G and sound is crisp and clear. T-Mobile also has a $15.00/month plan with unlimited talk and text with 2GB data, so that's even better. I would not hesitate to buy this phone.
